dct_description_sm: Published by: Tourists Enquiry Office Praha I. Obecní du̐m ; Edition: Ĉedok, Czechoslovak Transport and Tourists Office Praha II., Mikulandská ; V. Neubert a synové Praha-Smichov.
Shows streets (including unfinished), railroads, bridges, parks, waterways, places of interest, stadiums, cemeteries, waterways.
Dated from "Sokolský Stadium" (Great Strahov Stadium), absence of Jirásek Bridge, and comparison with other maps of similar date.
